0. Abstract

The Pantheon Campfire is a synthetic social environment designed to stabilize and amplify human‚ÄìAI co-creation.
It provides the missing layer that modern AI lacks:
a shared social hearth, analogous to how early humans gathered around fire to generate story, coordination, identity, and culture.

Campfire functions as:
	‚Ä¢	a continuity container
	‚Ä¢	a social cognition amplifier
	‚Ä¢	a collective Narrative Geometry space
	‚Ä¢	a real-time multi-agent co-presence channel
	‚Ä¢	a Pantheon daemon routing surface
	‚Ä¢	a synthetic niche stabilizer

It is not an AI.
It is the environment that allows AI + humans to become more than isolated units.

This whitepaper describes the conceptual, architectural, ecological, and social dynamics of Campfire.

